<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./quiz.css">
    <title>Consumption Habits Quiz</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>How sustainable are your consumption habits?</h1>
        <form id="quizForm">
            <div class="question">
                <p>1. How often do you buy second-hand or pre-owned items?</p>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q1" value="A"> A. Always</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q1" value="B"> B. Often</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q1" value="C"> C. Sometimes</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q1" value="D"> D. Rarely</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q1" value="E"> E. Never</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q1" value="F"> F. I’ve never thought about it</label>
            </div>
            <div class="question">
                <p>2. When shopping for groceries, do you check for local or organic options?</p>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q2" value="A"> A. Always</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q2" value="B"> B. Often</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q2" value="C"> C. Sometimes</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q2" value="D"> D. Rarely</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q2" value="E"> E. Never</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q2" value="F"> F. I don’t pay attention to labels</label>
            </div>
            <div class="question">
                <p>3. Do you avoid products with excessive packaging?</p>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q3" value="A"> A. Always</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q3" value="B"> B. Often</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q3" value="C"> C. Sometimes</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q3" value="D"> D. Rarely</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q3" value="E"> E. Never</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q3" value="F"> F. Packaging doesn’t concern me</label>
            </div>
            <div class="question">
                <p>4. Do you research brands to ensure they are ethical?</p>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q4" value="A"> A. Always</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q4" value="B"> B. Often</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q4" value="C"> C. Sometimes</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q4" value="D"> D. Rarely</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q4" value="E"> E. Never</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q4" value="F"> F. I don’t have time to research</label>
            </div>
            <div class="question">
                <p>5. How often do you choose public transport, bike, or walk instead of driving?</p>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q5" value="A"> A. Always</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q5" value="B"> B. Often</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q5" value="C"> C. Sometimes</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q5" value="D"> D. Rarely</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q5" value="E"> E. Never</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q5" value="F"> F. I don’t have other options</label>
            </div>
            <div class="question">
                <p>6. When buying clothes, do you prioritize quality over quantity?</p>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q6" value="A"> A. Always</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q6" value="B"> B. Often</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q6" value="C"> C. Sometimes</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q6" value="D"> D. Rarely</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q6" value="E"> E. Never</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q6" value="F"> F. I just buy what I like</label>
            </div>
            <div class="question">
                <p>7. Do you bring your own reusable bags, bottles, or containers when shopping or eating out?</p>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q7" value="A"> A. Always</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q7" value="B"> B. Often</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q7" value="C"> C. Sometimes</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q7" value="D"> D. Rarely</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q7" value="E"> E. Never</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q7" value="F"> F. I forget most of the time</label>
            </div>
            <div class="question">
                <p>8. Do you actively reduce your energy consumption at home?</p>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q8" value="A"> A. Always</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q8" value="B"> B. Often</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q8" value="C"> C. Sometimes</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q8" value="D"> D. Rarely</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q8" value="E"> E. Never</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q8" value="F"> F. I don’t think about it</label>
            </div>
            <div class="question">
                <p>9. How often do you donate or recycle items you no longer need?</p>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q9" value="A"> A. Always</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q9" value="B"> B. Often</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q9" value="C"> C. Sometimes</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q9" value="D"> D. Rarely</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q9" value="E"> E. Never</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q9" value="F"> F. I just throw things away</label>
            </div>
            <div class="question">
                <p>10. Do you educate yourself or others about responsible consumption practices?</p>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q10" value="A"> A. Always</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q10" value="B"> B. Often</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q10" value="C"> C. Sometimes</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q10" value="D"> D. Rarely</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q10" value="E"> E. Never</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q10" value="F"> F. I don’t think it’s necessary</label>
            </div>
            <button type="button" onclick="calculateResult()">Submit</button>
        </form>
        <div id="result" class="result"></div>
      </div>
      <script src="./quiz.js"></script>
  </body>
  </html>

